@model OmniBizAI.ViewModels.ProcurementListViewModel
@using OmniBizAI.Models.Entities.Enums
@using OmniBizAI.Helpers
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Đề xuất mua sắm";
    ViewData["Breadcrumb"] = "<span>Tài chính</span> <i class='fa-solid fa-chevron-right' style='font-size:.6rem;margin:0 6px;color:var(--text-muted)'></i> <span>Đề xuất mua sắm</span>";
    
    var totalEstimated = Model.Items.Sum(i => i.TotalEstimated);
    var pendingCount = Model.Items.Count(i => i.Status == "Submitted");
    var approvedCount = Model.Items.Count(i => i.Status == "Approved");
}

<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4 flex-wrap gap-2">
    <div>
        <h4 class="page-title mb-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping me-2 text-primary"></i>Đề xuất mua sắm</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0" style="font-size:.82rem">Quản lý và theo dõi các đề xuất mua sắm của doanh nghiệp</p>
    </div>
    <a asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus me-2"></i>Tạo đề xuất</a>
</div>

<!-- Stat cards -->
<div class="row g-3 mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon blue"><i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open"></i></div>
            <div class="stat-value">@Model.TotalCount</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tổng đề xuất</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon orange"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
            <div class="stat-value">@pendingCount</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Chờ phê duyệt</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon green"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></div>
            <div class="stat-value">@approvedCount</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Đã phê duyệt</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon purple"><i class="fa-solid fa-tags"></i></div>
            <div class="stat-value">@totalEstimated.ToString("N0") ₫</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tổng giá trị dự kiến</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Filters -->
<div class="content-card mb-4">
    <div class="card-body-custom">
        <form method="get" class="row g-3 align-items-end">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <label class="form-label">Tìm kiếm</label>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-text bg-light border-end-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" name="search" value="@Model.SearchTerm" class="form-control border-start-0 bg-light" placeholder="Tìm theo mã hoặc tiêu đề..." />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                <label class="form-label">Trạng thái</label>
                <select name="status" class="form-select bg-light">
                    <option value="">-- Tất cả trạng thái --</option>
                    @foreach(var s in EnumHelper.GetSelectList<ProcurementStatus>(Model.StatusFilter))
                    {
                        <option value="@s.Value" selected="@s.Selected">@s.Text</option>
                    }
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100"><i class="fa-solid fa-filter me-2"></i>Lọc danh sách</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Table list -->
<div class="content-card">
    <div class="card-body-custom p-0">
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-hover align-middle mb-0" style="min-width: 800px;">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th class="ps-4" style="width: 120px;">Mã đề xuất</th>
                        <th>Tiêu đề</th>
                        <th>Phòng ban</th>
                        <th>Người đề xuất</th>
                        <th>Ước tính</th>
                        <th>Trạng thái</th>
                        <th>Cần trước ngày</th>
                        <th class="pe-4 text-end" style="width: 100px;">Thao tác</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    @foreach (var p in Model.Items) {
                        var badgeCls = p.Status switch {
                            "Approved" => "badge-on-track",
                            "Draft" => "badge-at-risk",
                            "Submitted" => "badge-behind",
                            "Cancelled" => "badge-behind",
                            "Ordered" => "badge-on-track",
                            "Received" => "badge-on-track",
                            _ => "badge-at-risk"
                        };
                        <tr>
                            <td class="ps-4">
                                <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@p.Id" class="fw-bold text-decoration-none" style="color:var(--apple-blue)">@p.RequestNo</a>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="fw-medium text-dark">@p.Title</div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="text-secondary small"><i class="fa-regular fa-building me-1"></i>@(p.Department ?? "—")</span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="small">@p.RequestedBy</span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="fw-semibold text-primary">@p.TotalEstimated.ToString("N0") ₫</span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="status-badge-soft @badgeCls">
                                    <span class="status-dot"></span>
                                    @(EnumHelper.Label<ProcurementStatus>(p.Status))
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="text-muted small"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-check me-1"></i>@(p.NeededByDate?.ToString("dd/MM/yyyy") ?? "—")</span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="pe-4 text-end">
                                <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@p.Id" class="btn btn-light btn-sm border" title="Xem chi tiết">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-eye text-secondary"></i>
                                </a>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    }
                    @if (!Model.Items.Any()) {
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="8" class="text-center py-5 text-muted">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-inbox fa-3x mb-3 d-block opacity-40"></i>
                                Chưa có đề xuất mua sắm nào được tạo
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    }
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
